summary: My Name is Jan Rodenrijs and Iwork under the name Jarod Art. I am a very creative person. Creating things is my breath of life. My goal is also to make people more aware of the importance of well designed promotional material to create a more professional image for a company. Next to that I have my personal goal of achieving recognition as a graphic artist
